name: Yellow Crane Tower
description:
The legend of the Yellow Crane Tower has a long history. It has been accompanied by the Yellow Crane Tower, which has been destroyed and built repeatedly, and has been enriched and extended continuously. Mysterious, strange, wonderful, tactful and moving. It not only has high historical and cultural value, but also has distinctive literary value and strong regional cultural color. It can be called the treasure of Wuhan folk culture. The 
legend of the Yellow Crane Tower comes from the folk and contains profound and rich traditional cultural connotations such as Xiandao culture, folk wisdom, literati flow rhyme and so on.
